 I am curious about how the CVAT tool converts videos to individual frames
 
 Three different ways. Briefly are zip chunks, video chunks and original video where the chunks are lazy-prepared "on the fly" with using special metainformation that is created during task creating. Chunks are automatically decoded client-side with js ffmpeg or js archiver. Also all chunks are stored in original (necessary when export a dataset) and compressed (necessary to optimize client-server streaming) quality
